title: My 5 Scans - April 2014 (gnv64)
description:
In this torrent, I am sharing with you some of the books scanned by me, actually they are 3 books & 2 magazine articles. All have OCR, the books have bookmarks & covers:

1. Classic Ghost Stories
2. Dialogue with Death by Eknath Easwaran
3. Hinduism - An Introduction by Shakunthala Jagannathan

4. Albums & Singles of 2013 from Rolling Stone Jan 14
5. Top 10 of Everything from Digit March 14
